    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Fulfill paid orders with Shopify and MySQL in real time\n\n**Pattern:** Order Fulfillment · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nFulfill paid orders with Shopify and MySQL in real time. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual inventory is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Required Fields Present? → Route by Work Type → Process 'standard' → MySQL → Merge Routed Work → Tag Pipeline Metadata → Align Field Names → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to order fulfillment without manual effort\n- Anyone automating inventory in e-commerce\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Standardizes the process every time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: MySQL connection; Slack OAuth2; Twilio SID + token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
